cdata.name: RiptideCoin
cdata.desc:
Riptide project aims to ease the implementation of electronic payments for the Dispensary and Delivery servicesof theMarijuanaindustry. In order to be able to do that Riptide team will leverage the Ethereum blockchain toprovide a platformthat willsupport the transactions.

Riptide token (RIPT) is an ERC-20 token that will be used as a medium of exchange on the platform.
